{"tid":782683,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"學左兩個月唱歌到 唱歌夠境岩唔岩我 應唔應該學落去","createTime":"2018-08-17T02:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T05:01:53.000Z","uid":51261,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"eba5c9e07f04ceaebda4f63ecd8356e687f71d2f","tid":782683,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"我自己就9唱左年幾 直至學左唱歌 我先知自己係玩緊聲帶自殺行為 但唱歌真係洗唔少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kg3.qq.com/node/play?s=53FZ_Y5H1tDcp5ZV&amp;shareuid=609f9f832528328e37&amp;topsource=a0_pn201001006_z1_u222605553_l1_t1534473900__\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkg3.qq.com%2Fnode%2Fplay%3Fs%3D53FZ_Y5H1tDcp5ZV%26shareuid%3D609f9f832528328e37%26topsource%3Da0_pn201001006_z1_u222605553_l1_t1534473900__&d=L4FTUiLN5ihyH%2FVxxQXTtJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=fe1c6b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://kg3.qq.com/node/play?s=53FZ_Y5H1tDcp5ZV&amp;shareuid=609f9f832528328e37&amp;topsource=a0_pn201001006_z1_u222605553_l1_t1534473900__</a><br />\n<br />\n學左兩個月唱成咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係好鐘意唱歌 一唔唱個人就唔舒服 身痕 每日起馬都用2個鐘練"},{"pid":"e4323c5d677c6bf0dbfbde6560bd358c0eeaa3a4","tid":782683,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3182640337596dc879d777e80a52e5532c7b7a1a","tid":782683,"uid":122134,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"夠你老母境"},{"pid":"67e9b9a03b1d5e8aa6c53131e93e12a95f591e11","tid":782683,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:52:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b55f877889296eec15704ec99bff03bfdafeedc7","tid":782683,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"岩牙"},{"pid":"efe8244aa2f175a5376c7927640b8ee